GW20e buildout example
======================

This buildout can be used to setup development, testing, acceptance and 
production environments for Plone 4.x

Prequisites
-----------

  * Python 2.7

Optional virtual environment
----------------------------

Create a virtualenv environment for Python 2.7

    virtualenv-2.7 --no-site-packages .
    . ./bin/activate

Bootstrap development buildout
------------------------------

Add your development sources for mr.developer to buildout.cfg. Bootstrap and
run buildout on the development configuration:

    python bootstrap.py
    ./bin/buildout

